<TEXT>
<P>
 What does this mean? "Honor Thy Father and Mother: The True Story of the 
Menendez Murders" (Fox, April 18).Does that mean that all the testimony given 
under oath was lies? 
</P>
<P>
 Ruthie Maron, Newport Beach 
