 To order summer opera tickets by phone, call the box office at 
011-44-0273-813813. For a little more than $4.50, you can have your name added 
to a mailing list for advance notice of productions. Information on the season 
and intermission dining is available by calling or writing the Glyndebourne 
Festival, Lewes, East Sussex, BN8 5UU. 
