<P>
 In the Weekend Escape on Yucca Valley ("Far Out Valley," April 3), you 
fortunately missed some bargains left for us locals: John's Place restaurant 
with two full-course dinners for $9 and Din Ho's and Steffano's, at $7 a plate. 
Then there's the 30-year-old Hi-Desert Nature Museum, which places wildflowers 
next to the (illustrations by desert naturalist) Henry Mockel. Here we call 
