Mirada. 
</P>
<P>
 The Argonauts' Kathy Moore (4-4) struck out four and gave up one earned run 
and three hits. Catcher Jennifer Johnson was named tournament MVP, and Moore, 
Griffin and White were named to the all-tournament team for Garden Grove 
(13-11). 
</P>
