<HEADLINE>
<P>
BARCELONA PIANIST WINS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Barcelona-born pianist Alicia de Larrocha was awarded one of eight Spain's 
