ORANGE COUNTY BRIEFLY: PRINTRONIX REPORTS PROFIT OF $1.9 MILLION FOR FISCAL '94 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Printronix Inc., a computer printer manufacturer, reported profit of $1.9 
million, or 56 cents a share, for the fiscal year ended March 25.That 
contrasted with a loss of $2.3 million, or 76 cents a share, for the previous 
year. Sales rose 14% to $107.4 million from $93.9 million. For the fourth 
quarter, profit was up 8% from the same period a year earlier to $917,000, or 
28 cents a share, from $851,000, or 27 cents a share. Three-month sales 
increased 31% to $30.5 million from $23.2 million. 
