Japan than just its cars. The Japanese-based truck importer on Monday will 
donate 50 two-volume sets of "Japan: An Illustrated Encyclopedia" to schools in 
Brea and Los Alamitos, for use in world culture and Japanese language programs. 
. . . They're much needed, says Masako White, who teaches Japanese at Brea 
Olinda High School: "It is difficult for my students to find research materials 
on Japan." 
