Christopher "some ideas" of his own late today. 
</P>
<P>
 Christopher is also seeking a detailed account from Assad of a new arms deal 
concluded last week with Russia. 
</P>
<P>
 Christopher wants to know if Syria will be getting missiles from Moscow and if 
so, of what range. 
