counties to professional and scientific workers would increase slightly more 
than 4% in the first two years of the contract, which is retroactive to July, 
1993. 
</P>
<P>
 Total base pay for workers in the other two bargaining units will rise 
slightly more than 6% for the first two years of the deal, Yasuda said. 
